decks.notes: The deck revolves around utilizing graveyard recursion and combo pieces to generate powerful synergies and overwhelming card advantage. It aims to quickly assemble its combo pieces and disrupt the opponent through hand disruption and removal spells. The commander, Old Stickfingers, allows for efficient graveyard manipulation, providing additional value from discarded cards. The deck includes a variety of tutors and card draw options to ensure consistency and find key combo pieces. It also incorporates ramp spells and mana acceleration to facilitate faster plays. The deck thrives on resource management and careful planning, leveraging its graveyard and spell selection to set up game-winning combos and control the board state.

This deck focuses on aggressive gameplay and overwhelming the opponent with quick and efficient creatures and burn spells. The main strategy revolves around dealing direct damage to the opponent's life total while also controlling the board with removal spells. The commander, Rem Karolus, synergizes well with small creatures and provides additional value through his abilities. The deck includes a mix of efficient burn spells like Lightning Bolt and Flame Slash, along with versatile creatures like Bonecrusher Giant and Skyclave Apparition. It also features impactful cards such as Blood Moon and Stoneforge Mystic to disrupt the opponent's game plan. The mana base consists of a combination of dual lands and fetch lands to ensure consistency and access to the desired colors.
